author: GameSpot
description:
Robbie Daymond (Persona 5, Final Fantasy XV, Cyberpunk 2077) dives into early gaming memories, from Pitfall to Zelda: Wind Waker and Final Fantasy X. He breaks down how voice acting led him to create his own outrageous dating sim, Date Everything.  We get into Dreamcast imports, Overwatch addiction, competitive gaming pain, and what it really takes to build a game from scratch with your friends.
